                "answer": "Ta có\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/381f4baa-1663-4c5b-afa7-e5eeb3db79f7.png\"/>\n<br>Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/63b013dc-dcf4-465e-a1db-7397d6889aff.png\"/> chia cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/418d073e-6751-45a2-8b85-eff23ec4f200.png\"/> dư là 9 nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/2ec60a35-7964-4375-97a8-97740f563ef1.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/e5031442-f103-4b7c-a824-0308f46ba4b8.png\"/>\n<br>Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/a6d965f0-02c6-4a9f-952f-928205c9a57e.png\"/> chia cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/3e8ab08c-ba51-4f09-bef5-3a3ec8ce1ba1.png\"/> dư là 2 nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0c33ebbe-c904-47f7-9a2a-898a3d48fef9.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/f3a1d75b-645e-42b2-b8d4-9c5ec11135f1.png\"/>\n<br>Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/279ca9dc-5104-411f-833c-4e504f844b6f.png\"/> chia cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/15f05fc6-7b56-4f97-b73e-c2996d466ea0.png\"/> có thương là <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/97049b04-08b1-46e0-bb01-5fd02e4ca057.png\"/> và còn dư nên\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/62642ddb-dbe9-44c1-a582-ba68bb7874bd.png\"/>\n<br>Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/4e79072e-ef87-45ca-b39f-8a13ff58c921.png\"/>  nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/c3152183-8811-47f8-afb8-016f76656889.png\"/>  (1)\n<br>Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/6dd487da-54ff-41f8-8ed0-9f11cbd661a2.png\"/> nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/8881a32f-6230-40b2-b730-e03035dde35b.png\"/>   (2)\n<br>Lấy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/bcc6a391-c0fa-41db-903c-125449a75778.png\"/> vế theo vế ta có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/20b92a5d-fc2d-4ee0-a190-cb4fdff8d0eb.png\"/> suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/511607ec-01c0-4cc2-9a0d-7c6fe8d3992e.png\"/>. Thay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/b3be90e9-8915-4dd0-8dac-f9e162ef9668.png\"/> vào (1) ta có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/bb15692c-df7f-4363-b811-3cbb29131ce1.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/ef54548f-9d46-491f-bbca-15cce474b223.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/28966306-029f-46c5-8328-0ff78331cf52.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/7fcebd97-418d-42bd-aa5d-9b46ce128b44.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/11436f63-aa85-4fdd-abff-e5c1e53583e6.png\"/>\n<br>Vậy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/93cf61c7-6975-4d73-8a40-103080e5a8db.png\"/>\n",
